<h1>Implementing The Tealium Universal Tag</h1>

<p>The script is generated dynamically based on your configuration selections 
and includes your Data Layer. The Data Layer is generated from the variables 
listed in the Variables tab.</p>

<h2>To place the code on your website:</h2>

<ol>
    <li> Ensure you are are getting the code for the correct environment by 
looking at the navigation on the left. (Dev, QA, Prod)</li>
    <li> Click on the "Tealium Script" tab above.</li>
    <li> Click and drag to select all the code.</li>
    <li> Copy the code.</li>
    <li> Navigate to the appropriate webpage, and paste 
the code after the opening BODY tag.</li>
</ol>

